      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONE MARGARITA (5) has been thereabouts without winning, the latest finishing fourth (17.33) off a tricky draw at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 5. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. AGENT TWENTY ONE (7) copped a check but raced on speed and boxed on well, finishing a 2 length third (20.21) in a Grade 6 at Angle Park. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. GIN AND JUICE (1) progressive type who recorded his 11th career win last time out (22.92) at Gawler. Solid record here including two wins. Overall strike-rate good and can feature with the right run. REDTAIL COCKATOO (4) will be hard to beat with a drop in journey.",
